      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Real Property Tax</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Real properties located within the City limits are subject to taxation unless specifically exempted. Each property is reassessed every three years by the <strong>State Department of Assessments and Taxation</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        The real property tax is levied annually on all taxable land and improvements. The City's current tax rate is <strong>$0.625 per $100 of assessed value</strong>. Real property taxes are assessed and billed on <strong>July 1</strong> of each year.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        A property owner of an owner-occupied property may be eligible for a Homeowners' Tax Credit from the State. Contact the State Department of Assessments and Taxation for eligibility details.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800">Property Tax Bills must be paid in the <strong>full amount due</strong>, including any interest and penalty charges.</p>
      </div>

